For Autocaption to work, the fonts .ttf files needs to be under 
/workspace/ComfyUI/custom_nodes/ComfyUI-Whispery/fonts so the node "Add Subtitles to Frames" can find them. So we may need duplicates in both "Text Overlay" and "Whisper" custom_nodes folders, or create symlinks and try it that way (to avoid duplicates) = if we ever want to add new fonts.
Somebody's watching me, it's my anxiety.

For TextOverlay to work, the name of the Font needs to be inserted into font input of the TextOverlay node. And the fonts .ttf file needs to be under 
/workspace/ComfyUI/custom_nodes/ComfyUI-TextOverlay/fonts so the node can find them.

List of Hex Colors for Text on Images and Videos
Here are **15 hex colors** carefully selected for this context:

1. #FFFFFF
** - White  
   Perfect for dark or colorful backgrounds, offering maximum contrast and visibility.

2. #000000
** - Black  
   Ideal for light backgrounds, providing strong contrast and a classic look.

3. #FFD700
** - Gold  
   Warm and vibrant, works well on both light and dark backgrounds.

4. #FF4500
** - Orange-Red  
   Bold and attention-grabbing, suitable for many background types.

5. #00BFFF - Deep Sky Blue  
   Fresh and modern, visible on both light and dark surfaces.

6. #228B22
** - Forest Green  
   Deep and contrasting, great for light or nature-themed backgrounds.

7. #FF1493 - Deep Pink  
   Vivid and eye-catching, stands out on colorful or light backgrounds.

8. #4B0082 - Indigo  
   Dark and elegant, pairs well with light or pastel backgrounds.

9. #DDFF00 - Lime Yellow  
   Highly visible, though use caution on light backgrounds.

10. #DC143C - Crimson  
    Intense and rich, offers good contrast on light or neutral backgrounds.

11. #2F20C1 - Blue  
    Neutral and subtle, balances well on both light and dark backgrounds.

12. #00FF00 - Lime Green  
    Bright and visible, especially effective on dark or black backgrounds.

13. #E6E6FA - Lavender  
    Soft and elegant, works nicely on dark or contrasting backgrounds.
14. #85FFED - Cyan
15. #9C82C2 - Dusty Lavender
